{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I started juggling a long time ago,"},{"time":3000,"text":"but long before that, I was a golfer, and that's what I was, a golfer."},{"time":9000,"text":"And as a golfer and as a kid,"},{"time":13000,"text":"one of the things that really sort of seeped into my pores,"},{"time":16000,"text":"that I sort of lived my whole life, is process."},{"time":19000,"text":"And it's the process of learning things."},{"time":21000,"text":"One of the great things was that my father was an avid golfer, but he was lefty."},{"time":25000,"text":"And he had a real passion for golf,"},{"time":27000,"text":"and he also created this whole mythology"},{"time":30000,"text":"about Ben Hogan and various things."},{"time":32000,"text":"Well, I learned a lot about interesting things"},{"time":34000,"text":"that I knew nothing about at the time, but grew to know stuff about."},{"time":38000,"text":"And that was the mythology of skill."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41000,"text":"So, one of the things that I love to do is to explore skill."},{"time":44000,"text":"And since Richard put me on this whole thing with music --"},{"time":48000,"text":"I'm supposed to actually be doing a project with Tod Machover"},{"time":51000,"text":"with the MIT Media Lab -- it relates a lot to music."},{"time":53000,"text":"But Tod couldn't come and the project is sort of somewhere,"},{"time":56000,"text":"I'm not sure whether it's happening the way we thought, or not."},{"time":59000,"text":"But I'm going to explore skill, and juggling,"},{"time":63000,"text":"and basically visual music, I guess."},{"time":70000,"text":"OK, you can start the music, thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":250000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":253000,"text":"Thanks. Thank you. Now, juggling can be a lot of fun;"},{"time":262000,"text":"play with skill and play with space, play with rhythm."},{"time":266000,"text":"And you can turn the mike on now. I'm going to do a couple of pieces."},{"time":269000,"text":"I do a big piece in a triangle"},{"time":272000,"text":"and these are three sections from it."},{"time":274000,"text":"Part of the challenge was to try to understand rhythm and space"},{"time":277000,"text":"using not just my hands -- because a lot of juggling is hand-oriented --"},{"time":281000,"text":"but using the rhythm of my body and feet,"},{"time":283000,"text":"and controlling the balls with my feet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":364000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":369000,"text":"Thanks. Now, this next section was an attempt to explore space."},{"time":377000,"text":"You see, I think Richard said something about people that are against something."},{"time":381000,"text":"Well, a lot of people think jugglers defy gravity or do stuff."},{"time":387000,"text":"Well, I kind of, from my childhood and golf and all that,"},{"time":390000,"text":"it's a process of joining with forces."},{"time":393000,"text":"And so what I'd like to do is try to figure out"},{"time":394000,"text":"how to join with the space through the technique."},{"time":397000,"text":"So juggling gravity -- up, down."},{"time":402000,"text":"If you figure out what up and down really are,"},{"time":409000,"text":"it's a complex physical set of skills"},{"time":411000,"text":"to be able to throw a ball down and up and everything,"},{"time":414000,"text":"but then you add in sideways."}]},{"cues":[{"time":439000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":445000,"text":"Now, I look at it somewhat as a way -- when you learn juggling"},{"time":450000,"text":"what you learn is how to feel with your eyes, and see with your hands"},{"time":454000,"text":"because you're not looking at your hands,"},{"time":456000,"text":"you're looking at where the balls are or you're looking at the audience."},{"time":459000,"text":"So this next part is really a way of understanding space and rhythm,"},{"time":464000,"text":"with the obvious reference to the feet,"},{"time":466000,"text":"but it's also time -- where the feet were, where the balls were."}]},{"cues":[{"time":547000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":557000,"text":"Thanks. So, visual music: rhythm and complexity."},{"time":562000,"text":"I'm going to build towards complexity now."},{"time":564000,"text":"Juggling three balls is simple and normal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":568000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":570000,"text":"Excuse me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":572000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":574000,"text":"We're jugglers, OK. And remember, you're transposing,"},{"time":577000,"text":"you're getting into a subculture here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":579000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":580000,"text":"And juggling -- the balls cross and all that."},{"time":583000,"text":"OK, if you keep them in their assigned paths you get parallel lines"},{"time":587000,"text":"of different heights, but then hopefully even rhythm."},{"time":590000,"text":"And you can change the rhythm -- good, Michael."},{"time":594000,"text":"You can change the rhythm, if you get out of the lights."},{"time":596000,"text":"OK? Change the rhythm, so it's even."},{"time":600000,"text":"Or you can go back and change the height. Now, skill."},{"time":606000,"text":"But you're boxed in, if you can only do it up and down that way."},{"time":610000,"text":"So, you've got to go after the space down there."},{"time":619000,"text":"OK, then you've got to combine them,"},{"time":622000,"text":"because then you have the whole spatial palette in front of you."},{"time":631000,"text":"And then you get crazy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":641000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":645000,"text":"Now, I'm actually going to ask you to try something,"},{"time":649000,"text":"so you've got to pay attention. Complexity:"},{"time":652000,"text":"if you spend enough time doing something, time slows down"},{"time":656000,"text":"or your skill increases, so your perceptions change."},{"time":659000,"text":"It's learning skills -- like being in a high-speed car crash."},{"time":663000,"text":"Things slow down as you learn, as you learn, as you learn."},{"time":666000,"text":"You may not be able to affect it, it almost drifts on you. It goes."},{"time":670000,"text":"But that's the closest approximation I can have to it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":673000,"text":"So, complexity. Now, how many here are jugglers?"},{"time":679000,"text":"OK, so most of you are going to have a similar reaction to this."},{"time":690000,"text":"OK? And whoever laughed there --"},{"time":692000,"text":"you understood it completely, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":694000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":696000,"text":"No, it looks like a mess. It looks like a mess with a guy there,"},{"time":699000,"text":"who's got his hands around that mess, OK."},{"time":702000,"text":"Well, that's what juggling is about, right?"},{"time":704000,"text":"It's being able to do something that other people can't do or can't understand."},{"time":708000,"text":"All right. So, that's one way of doing it, which is five balls down."},{"time":711000,"text":"OK? Another way is the outside."},{"time":716000,"text":"And you could play with the rhythm."},{"time":720000,"text":"Same pattern."},{"time":723000,"text":"Make it faster and smaller."},{"time":726000,"text":"Make it wider."},{"time":729000,"text":"Make it narrower."},{"time":734000,"text":"Bring it back up."},{"time":737000,"text":"OK. It's done. Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":740000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":743000,"text":"Now, what I wanted to get to is that you're all very bright, very tactile."},{"time":750000,"text":"I have no idea how computer-oriented or three-dimensionally-oriented you are,"},{"time":755000,"text":"but let's try something."},{"time":757000,"text":"OK, so since you all don't understand what the five-ball pattern is,"},{"time":763000,"text":"I'm going to give you a little clue."},{"time":776000,"text":"Enough of a clue? So, you get the pattern, right? OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":780000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":783000,"text":"You're not getting off that easy. All right?"},{"time":788000,"text":"Now, do me a favor: follow the ball that I ask you to follow."},{"time":793000,"text":"Green."},{"time":795000,"text":"Yellow."},{"time":797000,"text":"Pink."},{"time":799000,"text":"White."},{"time":802000,"text":"OK, you can do that? Yeah? OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":805000,"text":"Now, let's actually learn something."},{"time":808000,"text":"Actually, let me put you in that area of learning, which is very insecure."},{"time":813000,"text":"You want to do it? Yeah? OK."},{"time":817000,"text":"Hands out in front of you. Palms up, together."},{"time":822000,"text":"What you're going to learn is this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":825000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":827000,"text":"OK? So what I want you to do is just listen to me and do it."},{"time":831000,"text":"Index finger, middle finger, ring, little."},{"time":834000,"text":"Little, ring, middle, index. And then open."},{"time":838000,"text":"Finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger."},{"time":842000,"text":"A little bit faster."},{"time":844000,"text":"Finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger."},{"time":846000,"text":"Finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger."}]},{"cues":[{"time":850000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":851000,"text":"All right. A lot of different learning processes going on in here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":855000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":857000,"text":"One learning process that I see is this --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":860000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":862000,"text":"OK. Another learning process that I see is this --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":867000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":870000,"text":"OK. So, everybody take a deep breath in, breath out. OK."},{"time":875000,"text":"Now, one more time, and --"},{"time":877000,"text":"finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger. Open."},{"time":881000,"text":"Finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger. OK."},{"time":884000,"text":"Shake your hands out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":886000,"text":"Now, I assume a lot of you spend a lot of time at a computer."},{"time":889000,"text":"OK? So, what you're doing is, you're going la, la, la,"},{"time":892000,"text":"and you're getting this. OK?"},{"time":894000,"text":"So that's exactly what I'm going to ask you to do,"},{"time":896000,"text":"but in a slightly different way. You're going to combine it."},{"time":899000,"text":"So what I want you to do is -- fingers."},{"time":902000,"text":"I'll tell you what to do with your fingers, same thing."},{"time":904000,"text":"But I want you to do is also, with your eyes,"},{"time":907000,"text":"is follow the colored ball that I ask you to follow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":910000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":912000,"text":"OK? Here we go."},{"time":914000,"text":"So, we're going to start off looking at the white ball --"},{"time":916000,"text":"and I'm going to tell you which color,"},{"time":918000,"text":"and I'm also going to tell you to go with your fingers. OK?"},{"time":920000,"text":"So white ball and --"},{"time":923000,"text":"finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger. Pink."},{"time":928000,"text":"Finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger. Green."},{"time":933000,"text":"Finger, finger, finger, finger. Yellow."},{"time":936000,"text":"Finger, finger, finger, pink or finger."},{"time":939000,"text":"Pink, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger, finger."},{"time":944000,"text":"All right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":946000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":949000,"text":"How did you do? Well? OK. The reason I wanted you to do this is"},{"time":954000,"text":"because that's actually what most people face throughout their lives,"},{"time":959000,"text":"a moment of learning, a moment of challenge."},{"time":962000,"text":"It's a moment that you can't make sense of."},{"time":964000,"text":"Why the hell should I learn this? OK?"},{"time":967000,"text":"Does it really have anything to do with anything in my life?"},{"time":971000,"text":"You know, I can't decipher -- is it fun? Is it challenging? Am I supposed to cheat?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":974000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":975000,"text":"You know, what are you supposed to do?"},{"time":977000,"text":"You've got somebody up here who is the operative principle"},{"time":981000,"text":"of doing that for his whole life. OK?"},{"time":984000,"text":"Trying to figure that stuff out. But is it going to get you anywhere?"},{"time":987000,"text":"It's just a moment. That's all it is, a moment. OK?"},{"time":990000,"text":"I'm going to change the script for one second. Just let me do this."},{"time":993000,"text":"I don't need music for it. Talking about time in a moment."},{"time":996000,"text":"There's a piece that I recently developed which was all about that,"},{"time":1000000,"text":"a moment. And what I do as a creative artist"},{"time":1003000,"text":"is I develop vocabularies or languages of moving objects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1007000,"text":"What I've done for you here, I developed a lot of those tricks"},{"time":1010000,"text":"and I put the choreography together,"},{"time":1012000,"text":"but they're not original techniques."},{"time":1014000,"text":"Now, I'm going to start showing you some original techniques"},{"time":1016000,"text":"that come from the work that I've developed. OK?"},{"time":1018000,"text":"So, a moment, how would you define a moment?"},{"time":1021000,"text":"Well, as a juggler, what I wanted to do was create something"},{"time":1026000,"text":"that was representational of a moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1032000,"text":"Ahhh."},{"time":1035000,"text":"All right, I'm going to get on my knees and do it."},{"time":1038000,"text":"So, a moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1040000,"text":"(Rattling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1047000,"text":"OK? And then, what I did as a juggler was say,"},{"time":1050000,"text":"OK, what can I do to make that something"},{"time":1052000,"text":"that is dependent on something else, another dynamic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1061000,"text":"(Rattling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1071000,"text":"So, a moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1075000,"text":"(Rattling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1077000,"text":"Another moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1079000,"text":"(Rattling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1085000,"text":"Excuse me, still getting there. A moment that travels."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1090000,"text":"(Rattling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1096000,"text":"A moment -- no, we'll try that again. It separates, and comes back together."},{"time":1103000,"text":"Time. How can you look at time?"},{"time":1106000,"text":"And what do you dedicate it to, in exploring a particular thing?"},{"time":1110000,"text":"Well, obviously, there's something in here,"},{"time":1113000,"text":"and you can all have a guess as to what it is."},{"time":1115000,"text":"There's a mystery. There's a mystery in the moment."},{"time":1117000,"text":"And it has to settle. And then it's dependent on something else."},{"time":1121000,"text":"And then it comes to rest. Just a little thing about time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1129000,"text":"Now, this has expanded into a much bigger piece,"},{"time":1131000,"text":"because I use ramps of different parabolas that I roll the balls on"},{"time":1134000,"text":"while I'm keeping time with this."},{"time":1136000,"text":"But I just thought I'd talk about a moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1139000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1142000,"text":"All right. OK. Can we show the video of the triangle?"},{"time":1148000,"text":"Are we ready to do that? Yes?"},{"time":1150000,"text":"This is the piece that I told you about."},{"time":1152000,"text":"It's a much bigger piece that I do exploring the space of a geometric triangle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1211000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1216000,"text":"Thanks. The only thing I'll say about the last session is,"},{"time":1220000,"text":"you ever try juggling and driving the car with your knees"},{"time":1224000,"text":"at 120 miles an hour?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1226000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1228000,"text":"The only other thing is, it was a real shock."},{"time":1230000,"text":"I always drove motorcycles. And when I bought my first car, it shocked me"},{"time":1234000,"text":"that it cost three times more than my parents' house. Interesting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1239000,"text":"Anyway, balance:"},{"time":1241000,"text":"constant movement to find an approach to stillness."},{"time":1248000,"text":"Cheating."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1249000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1252000,"text":"Balance: making up the rules so you can't cheat,"},{"time":1256000,"text":"so you learn to approach stillness with different parts of your body."},{"time":1267000,"text":"To have a conversation with it. To speak. To listen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1277000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1278000,"text":"Hup. Now, it's dependent on rhythm,"},{"time":1281000,"text":"and keeping a center of balance. When it falls, going underneath."},{"time":1289000,"text":"So, there's a rhythm to it."},{"time":1293000,"text":"The rhythm can get much smaller."},{"time":1303000,"text":"As your skill increases, you learn to find those tinier spaces,"},{"time":1309000,"text":"those tinier movements. Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1313000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1317000,"text":"Now, I'm going to show you the beginnings of a piece"},{"time":1319000,"text":"that is about balance in some ways, and also --"},{"time":1326000,"text":"oh, actually, if you're bored, not here, here's one use for it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1332000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1342000,"text":"You can go with the \"Sticks One\" music."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1349000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1433000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1440000,"text":"Thanks. That has a certain kind of balance to it, which is all about plumb."},{"time":1446000,"text":"I apprenticed with a carpenter and learned about plumb, square and level."},{"time":1452000,"text":"And they influenced that, and this next piece, which I'll do a little segment of."},{"time":1455000,"text":"\"Two Sticks,\" you can go with it. Thanks."},{"time":1461000,"text":"Which is again exploring space, or the lines in space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1465000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1526000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1528000,"text":"Working with space and the lines in space in a different way."},{"time":1536000,"text":"Oh, let's see here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1569000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1571000,"text":"So, I'll come back to that in a second. But working with one ball,"},{"time":1576000,"text":"now, what if you attach something to it, or change it."},{"time":1583000,"text":"This is a little thing that I made"},{"time":1585000,"text":"because I really like the idea of curves and balls together."},{"time":1591000,"text":"And then creating space and the rhythm of space,"},{"time":1597000,"text":"using the surface of the balls, the surface of the arms."},{"time":1602000,"text":"Just a little toy. Which leads me to the next thing,"},{"time":1606000,"text":"which is --"},{"time":1608000,"text":"what have I got here? OK. All right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1621000,"text":"I'm actually leading up to something,"},{"time":1622000,"text":"the newest thing that I'm working on. This is not it."},{"time":1626000,"text":"This is exploring geometry and the rhythm of shape."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1675000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1682000,"text":"Now, what I just did was I worked with the mathematics --"},{"time":1685000,"text":"the diameter and the circumference."},{"time":1688000,"text":"Sometimes these pieces are mathematical, in that way"},{"time":1691000,"text":"that I look at a shape and say, what about if I use this and this and this."},{"time":1694000,"text":"Sometimes what happens in life affects my choice"},{"time":1699000,"text":"of objects that I try to work with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1701000,"text":"The next piece that I'm going to do -- which is the cylinders piece,"},{"time":1704000,"text":"if you want to get that up --"},{"time":1706000,"text":"it has to do with cylinder seals from about 5,000 years ago,"},{"time":1713000,"text":"which were stones with designs that were used to roll over wet clay"},{"time":1718000,"text":"with all sorts of great designs. I love ceramics and all of that."},{"time":1722000,"text":"It's a combination of that, the beauty of that, the shape,"},{"time":1726000,"text":"and the stories that were involved in it,"},{"time":1731000,"text":"as well as the fact that they protected the contents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1735000,"text":"The second influence on this piece came from recycling"},{"time":1740000,"text":"and looking into a tin can recycling bin"},{"time":1743000,"text":"and seeing all that beautiful emptiness."},{"time":1746000,"text":"So, if you want to go with the music for cylinders."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1749000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1919000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1922000,"text":"Talking about geometry and everything,"},{"time":1925000,"text":"if you take the circle and you split it in half --"},{"time":1930000,"text":"can you run \"S-Curve music?\""},{"time":1932000,"text":"I'm going to do just a short version of it."},{"time":1937000,"text":"Circles split in half and rotated, and mythology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1941000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":2039000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":2046000,"text":"Anyway, that piece also has a kinetic sculpture in the middle of it,"},{"time":2051000,"text":"and I dance around a small stage so --"},{"time":2054000,"text":"two minutes, just to end? The latest piece that I'm working on --"},{"time":2058000,"text":"what I love is that I never know what I'm working on, why I'm working on it."},{"time":2062000,"text":"They're not ideas, they're instincts."},{"time":2065000,"text":"And the latest thing that I'm working on --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":2067000,"text":"(Clattering) --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":2073000,"text":"is something really -- I don't know what it is yet."},{"time":2078000,"text":"And that's good. I like not to know for as long as possible."},{"time":2084000,"text":"Well, because then it tells me the truth,"},{"time":2086000,"text":"instead of me imposing the truth."},{"time":2089000,"text":"And what it is, is working with both positive and negative space"},{"time":2092000,"text":"but also with these curves."},{"time":2094000,"text":"And what it involves,"},{"time":2096000,"text":"and I don't know if my hands are too beaten up to do it or not,"},{"time":2099000,"text":"but I'll do a little bit of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2101000,"text":"It initially started off with me stacking these things,"},{"time":2104000,"text":"bunches of them, and then playing with the sense of space,"},{"time":2110000,"text":"of filling in the space. And then it started changing,"},{"time":2119000,"text":"and become folding on themselves."},{"time":2126000,"text":"And then changing levels."},{"time":2130000,"text":"Because my attempt is to make visual instruments,"},{"time":2135000,"text":"not to just make -- I'll try one other thing."},{"time":2140000,"text":"For work in three dimensions, with your perceptions of space and time."},{"time":2146000,"text":"Now, I don't know exactly where it's going,"},{"time":2148000,"text":"but I've got a bit of effort involved in this thing."},{"time":2150000,"text":"And it's going to change as I go through it."},{"time":2154000,"text":"But I really like it, it feels right."},{"time":2156000,"text":"This may not be the right shape, and -- look at this shape,"},{"time":2160000,"text":"and then I'll show you the first design I ever put to it,"},{"time":2164000,"text":"just to see, just to play,"},{"time":2167000,"text":"because I love all different kinds of things to play with."},{"time":2170000,"text":"Let's see here."},{"time":2172000,"text":"To work with the positive and negative in a different way."},{"time":2179000,"text":"And to change, and to change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2181000,"text":"So, I'm off in my new direction with this to explore rhythm and space."},{"time":2186000,"text":"We'll see what I come up with. Thanks for having me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2190000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}